        <h2>The AI Job Explosion</h2>
        <p>The job market is undergoing a seismic shift. Artificial Intelligence isn't just a buzzword anymore‚Äîit's reshaping industries, redefining job roles, and creating entirely new career paths that didn't exist five years ago.</p>
        
        <p>According to <strong>LinkedIn's Jobs on the Rise 2026</strong> report, AI-related positions dominate the fastest-growing roles. The data is clear: companies across every sector are racing to integrate AI into their operations.</p>

        <div class="job-rankings">
            <div class="job-rank">
                <div class="rank-number">#1</div>
                <div class="rank-content">
