                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="tip-icon">üéØ</span>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <strong>Apply AI outputs strategically</strong>
                    <p>Translate AI capabilities into business value and competitive advantage</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="tip-icon">üß†</span>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <strong>Bring human judgment</strong>
                    <p>Provide contextual understanding and ethical reasoning that machines cannot replicate</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>

